AIM deploy { "name": "vliedel/aim_modules/JpgToBmpModule", "git": "https://github.com/vliedel/aim_modules.git", "type": "background", "category": "", "description": "Transforms a jpeg as base64 string to bitmap", "long_description": "", "img_url": "", "android": { "package": "com.dobots.jpgtobmpmodule", "url": "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dobots.jpgtobmpmodule" }, "ports": [ { "name": "bmp", "dir": "out", "type": "intarray", "middleware": "default" }, { "name": "jpg", "dir": "in", "type": "std::string", "middleware": "default" } ] } 

sleep 1

AIM deploy { "name": "vliedel/aim_modules/ImageDisplayModule", "git": "https://github.com/vliedel/aim_modules.git", "type": "background", "category": "", "description": "Displays an image", "long_description": "", "img_url": "", "android": { "package": "com.dobots.imagedisplaymodule", "url": "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dobots.imagedisplaymodule" }, "ports": [ { "name": "image", "dir": "in", "type": "intarray", "middleware": "default" } ] } 

sleep 2

AIM start JpgToBmpModule 0

sleep 2

AIM start ImageDisplayModule 1

sleep 2

AIM connect local JpgToBmpModule 0 bmp local ImageDisplayModule 1 image

sleep 5

AIM connect raspberrypi_23 sendingtxtModule 0 txt local JpgToBmpModule 0 jpg

sleep 20

AIM data string bla/jdof/JpgToBmpModule 0 jpg
